        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Who knows!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "But the finest sport of all after her presentation was to hear her talk virtuously.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"One must, my dear, show one is somebody,\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000025_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000025_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"One mustn't be seen with doubtful people.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "The particulars of Becky's costume were in the newspapers-feathers, lappets, superb diamonds, and all the rest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000026_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000026_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You have only some of the best blood in England in your veins, and good principles and piety for your portion.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000026_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000026_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I, myself, the wife of a Baronet's younger brother, too, never thought of such a thing as going to Court-nor would other people, if good Queen Charlotte had been alive.\" In this way the worthy Rectoress consoled herself, and her daughters sighed and sat over the Peerage all night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Lady Steyne's carriage drove up to mr Rawdon Crawley's door, and the footman, instead of driving down the front of the house, as by his tremendous knocking he appeared to be inclined to do, relented and only delivered in a couple of cards, on which were engraven the names of the Marchioness of Steyne and the Countess of Gaunt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000027_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000027_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I say, how soon at the appearance of these grand court cards, did those poor little neglected deuces sink down to the bottom of the pack.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "She found him grinning over the bowl.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "She was discovered, and she blushed a little.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000029_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000029_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"You see your ladies have been here.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000029_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000029_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "How good of you!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000029_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000029_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I couldn't come before-I was in the kitchen making a pudding.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I heard you in the room overhead, where I have no doubt you were putting a little rouge on-you must give some of yours to my Lady Gaunt, whose complexion is quite preposterous-and I heard the bedroom door open, and then you came downstairs.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "About this who can tell?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"Well,\" said the old gentleman, twiddling round his wife's card, \"you are bent on becoming a fine lady.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000034_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000034_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You've got no money.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"You will get us a place,\" interposed Becky, \"as quick as possible.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"You've got no money, and you want to compete with those who have.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You will go to Gaunt House.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You give an old fellow no rest until you get there.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "It's not half so nice as here.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You'll be bored there.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I am.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "My wife is as gay as Lady Macbeth, and my daughters as cheerful as Regan and Goneril.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "I am an anchorite.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "You'll be asked to dinner next week.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000036_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000036_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "How the women will bully you!\" This was a very long speech for a man of few words like my Lord Steyne; nor was it the first which he uttered for Becky's benefit on that day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Her eyes filled with tears as she spoke, and she turned away her head.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"Men do that,\" Becky answered bitterly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "This caused the Lord Steyne to break out in another brief and energetic expression of anger, at which Rebecca held down her head the more and cried bitterly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "\"I could not help it.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "It was my only chance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000046_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000046_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "He would kill me if I told him what I have done. I have kept it a secret from everybody but you-and you forced it from me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Lord Steyne made no reply except by beating the devil's tattoo and biting his nails.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "At last he clapped his hat on his head and flung out of the room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000047_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000047_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "She burst out laughing once or twice to herself, as she sat at work, and sitting down to the piano, she rattled away a triumphant voluntary on the keys, which made the people pause under her window to listen to her brilliant music.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Rawdon heard Becky laughing in the night once or twice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "But the truth was that she was occupied with a great number of other thoughts.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-310_129055_000049_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/310/129055/310_129055_000049_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-310",
        "content": "Should she astonish Raggles by settling his account?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
